snippet.title: Spell Disk Survivor - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
"Spell Disk Survivor" is one of the game modes in "Spell Disk" where you survive against the endless waves of enemies. Craft overpowering builds using synergizing items and unlock new powers!

Developed by Sunpeak Games
